    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*&quot;Tip&quot; is a high-energy, 2D multiplayer platformer designed to keep players on the edge of their seats as they chase, dodge, and outwit each other. Set across vibrant levels, the game challenges players to tag or evade opponents while navigating challenging obstacles and mastering quick platforming skills. With a variety of game modes, every match feels fresh, allowing players to switch up their strategies based on the mode's objectives. There are lots of fun twists and modifiers to choose from, a few are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sudden Death Zoom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lava Rising</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These changes make the game much more chaotic and if you get bored there's a level editor and lot's of hidden mechanics you can use to your advantage!</p>",
